{
  "chapter": 17,
  "chapter_summary": "第十七章\"失而复得\"：庆功宴后，乌氏倮在密室向项少龙坦言乌家处境，赵人猜忌日深，赵穆与少原君虎视眈眈，乌应元已在海外部署后路。乌氏倮决定择日为项少龙与乌廷芳成亲，并赐宅院。陶方领项少龙前往新居，途中感慨自身际遇。宅内四婢春盈、夏盈、秋盈、冬盈跪迎，久别的侍妾婷芳氏在房中等候，二人久别重逢，情火重燃。次日清晨，陶方携项少龙入宫面见赵王，正式受任带兵卫之职，获三日假期。内侍臣吉光引他至后宫别楼，雅夫人赵雅主动现身，坦白脱离赵穆控制，愿以自身情报网为项少龙做内应，并揭露赵王与赵穆密谋利用项少龙对付乌家的阴谋，以及赵穆派人赴桑林村调查项少龙来历的危险。项少龙被赵雅的真心打动，接纳她为盟友与情人。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "乌氏倮",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "应元告诉了我整件事，少龙你不但剑术盖世，且智计过人，否则现在的局面会是截然相反。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "乌氏倮",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "应元告诉我少龙有秦人血统，换了以前，我必然非常不高兴，可是今天我却感到和你更接近。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "乌氏倮",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "text": "无论我为赵国立下多么大的功劳，赵人对我仍是猜忌甚深，今天连晋的事便是明证。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "乌氏倮",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "text": "想当年卫国商鞅入秦之前，秦人仍未脱戎狄之俗，父兄、子弟和姑媳、妯娌同寝一室，全赖商鞅改革变法，使秦一跃而成头等强国。可是看他这外国人得到什么遭遇，孝公一死，继位者立即把他车裂分尸。唉！现在我愈来愈相信应元所言，迟早我们会遭同一命运。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "text": "幸好现在少龙冒起，应可暂时消解对我们不利的形势。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "text": "只怕赵穆一计不成，再来一计，他定会设法把少龙陷害，少原君那家伙亦不可不防。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "乌氏倮",
      "listener": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "text": "他们想谋的是我乌族家业和财货、女人。哼！我乌氏倮岂是引颈就戮之辈，现在赵人已露出要对付我的痕迹，又有郭纵在旁推波助澜，我们要未雨绸缪，免得到时措手不及。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ying_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "乌应元",
      "listener": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "text": "爹放心吧！有了少龙，我们如虎添翼，赵人应不敢轻举妄动，何况这十年来，我无时无刻不利用往外之便，部署后路，现在已有点眉目，很快可把完整计划奉上，让爹考虑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "乌氏倮",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今天是你大喜的日子，这几天择个良日吉辰，立即给你和芳儿成亲，你可放心休息享乐，其他事都可暂搁一旁。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_shi_luo",
      "speaker_name": "乌氏倮",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "现在陶方会带你去见一个人，那是你应得的奖赏。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "假若不是遇上少龙，今天被赶出去的，不会是武黑而是我陶方。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "陶公究竟是否赵人，为何乌家父子这么信任你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "事实上我并不知道自己是什么人，若非上一代主人把我收养，恐怕我早饿死街头，所以对乌家纵使肝脑涂地，我陶方都没有半句怨言。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "由今晚开始，这房子就是你的寓所，孙小姐成为你的人后，也会搬到这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "好好享受吧！不过若孙小姐要来找你，连主人都挡她不住。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chun_ying",
      "speaker_name": "春盈",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小婢向公子请安。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_ying",
      "speaker_name": "夏盈",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "有人在房中等候公子。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "昨晚多喝两杯，又和两名歌舞姬胡混，现在头还有点疼痛，想不认老也不行，以前我试过连御七女仍面不改色的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "七个？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不信可以问大少爷，那晚他就在我隔壁，说整晚都听到她们的娇吟，唉！若有返老还童的仙丹就好哩。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我还以为赵雅昨晚定会来缠你，想不到竟然猜错。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "陶公请回府，少龙可交给本侯，我自会为他打点一切。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙初来甫到，定不习惯宫廷的规矩，不过现在大家是自己人，本侯自会看顾你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "多谢侯爷赏识，卑职对侯爷非常感激，若非侯爷提议，乌家怎肯将女儿许我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "哪里哪里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙今晚有没有什么特别的事情要办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "侯爷尽管吩咐，其他一切事我都可搁在一旁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "黄昏时我派人到乌府接少龙到我侯府吃顿晚饭，衣饰随随便便就可以，当是回家那样最好。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_guang",
      "speaker_name": "吉光",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大王对你不知多么恩宠，给了你三天假期，那时造妥官服，兵卫你穿起来定是威风凛凛，没有人比你更好看了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_guang",
      "text": "我现在可以走了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_guang",
      "speaker_name": "吉光",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "还要到一个地方去，兵卫请随小臣来。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_guang",
      "speaker_name": "吉光",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "兵卫请进，小臣在此恭候。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙！项少龙！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙！我们做个交易好吗？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "首先赵雅请你大人有大量，原谅她惨中赵穆这奸贼的毒计，差点害了你，也害了自己。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "赵雅还要多谢你，若非有你的出现，我可能永远离不开赵穆的控制，但由昨晚开始，想起他只令我作呕，从今以后，我绝不容他再沾我半根指头。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "也不容任何男人碰我，当然，唯一的例外是项少龙，他怎样碰都可以。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "夫人尚未说出你的交易条件。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我知少龙你故意吓人家，根本你再不恼我，还要装模作样。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "真的以后不碰别的男人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "当然是真的，不信把人家的心掏出来看吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "我昨晚虽曾狂欢一夜，可是现在仍给你逗得欲火焚身，只想看看你这交易里面最精彩的那件货色。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那件货色早是你的，现在赵雅来只是求你好心接收。我要付出的是雅夫人灵通的耳目，做你的哨兵和探子。",
      "tone": "媚笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "你是否暗示我会遇到很大的危险？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "一山怎能容二虎，这个道理多么简单，总有一天你会和赵穆正面冲突，赵雅这么有用的小兵，少龙怎可不欣然笑纳。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "原来脱离赵穆后，赵雅可变得如此厉害，本人决定将就点，收了你这件正货。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "记着是正而不是偏，离开邯郸后我要成为你的正妻之一。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "离开邯郸？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那是我们唯一的活路，否则不出一年，你和乌家将无一人能活命。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "雅儿你可否说清楚点？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "只要你肯一生一世疼爱人家，雅儿什么都听你的。",
      "tone": "深情",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "雅儿的呼吸时真美。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "继续赞美我吧！雅儿最爱给项郎逗哄。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "去你处还是我处？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "唉！雅儿比你更想哩！只是正事要紧，你和乌家正处于生死关头。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "昨天我被赵穆带回府中淫辱时，我趁他熟睡偷看他锁起来的秘密卷宗，发现了一张名单，都是乌家的人，列出名单上的人何时收取酬金，何时提供情报等所有有关细节，刚才我把这些人的名字默写出来，已放入你怀里去。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "你懂开锁吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人家自幼便受偷窃和刺探情报的训练，加上我的身份和肉体，所以雅儿常出使国外，收集情报。此事除王兄和赵穆外，无人晓得，现在人家什么都向你透露，你应知道人家的心意吧！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "我项少龙一诺千金，绝不会辜负你这可人儿。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "现在谁都知道你爱上我，他们不会怀疑你吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "放心吧！他们认定了我不会对任何男人长期迷恋，是天生的荡妇。何况我也姓赵，怎会助外姓人来对付自己血浓于水的家族？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "你真狠得起心来对付你们赵家的人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我对赵家已完全失望，他们不但排斥非赵国的人，更排斥外姓的赵人，这就是全无资历的赵括可以替代大将廉颇的原因，以致招来长平的大惨剧，令赵国由盛转衰，现在我只想随你远走高飞，不想终成亡国之奴，被贬作贱妓。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "乌应元在国外的活动，王兄等早有耳闻，还怀疑他曾与秦人接触，只不过乌氏倮控制我国近半的畜牧业，在赵国声望又高，家将数以万计，故王兄不敢轻举妄动，怕为此动摇根基，被他国乘虚而入。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "昨晚王兄和赵穆等在你战胜连晋后举行秘密会议，决定把你招纳过来，利用你对付乌家。后来王兄又召了我去，要我以美色迷惑你，教你不能自拔，而雅儿却自家知自家事，被迷惑的只是雅儿吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "暂时你还可拖延时间，因为赵穆的人这两天会出发到桑林村查探你的来历底细，肯定你没有问题才会重用你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "雅儿知你不但剑术盖世，智计更是厉害，现在人家把终身托付给你，祸福与共，你绝不可舍弃雅儿啊！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "现在我们来做一场戏，扮作我们刚刚欢好过，明白吗？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 363
    }
  ],
